  </header>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <h6>Need you be reminded that some answers will be sarcastic and tactless; some will be serious and add to your personal breadth of facts.  From the useless to the useful you will find some sort of a shift in your mental state.</h6>
  </div>

    <ul>
      {{#each model.questions as |question|}}
        <!-- {{question-popularity question}} -->
         {{question-display question=question update="update" destroyQuestion="destroyQuestion"}}
      {{/each}}
      <hr>
    {{new-question saveQuestion1="saveQuestion2"}}

    {{#link-to 'favorite-questions-route'}}View Your Favorite Questions{{/link-to}}

    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
